order by date

run(sql="
select  orderDate,
        count(distinct subOrderId) as total_orders,
        case when Channel = 'Direct' then 'organic_orders'
             when Channel = 'FB Channel' then 'fb_orders'
             when Channel = 'Re-Targeting Channel' then 'rt_orders'
             when Channel = 'Notification' then 'notif_orders'
             when Channel = 'Newsletter' then 'newsletter_orders'
             when Channel = 'SEO' then 'SEO_orders'
             when Channel = 'UnattributedUTM' then 'unattri_orders'
             when Channel = 'Other Marketing Channels' then 'omc_orders'
        end as channel,
        count(distinct subOrderId) as orders
from `temp.a` 
where orderDate>'2023-03-31'
group by orderDate, channel
order by orderDate
",1000)
